    {
      "id": "AOYh0y0koT-Ckb9RseEwt",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3814.8469034608347,
      "y": 2558.9783944195296,
      "width": 518.8187779017862,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bSf",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1514682950,
      "version": 937,
      "versionNonce": 87851782,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775372276008,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "TTL 的值一般为 64， Linux 将 MSL 设置为 30 秒，意\n味着 Linux 认为数据报文经过 64 个路由器的时间不会超\n过 30 秒，如果超过，就认为报文已经消失在网络中了。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "TTL 的值一般为 64， Linux 将 MSL 设置为 30 秒，意味着 Linux 认为数据报文经过 64 个路由器的时间不会超过 30 秒，如果超过，就认为报文已经消失在网络中了。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "xpqm7vpN2jdz0MST0tD17",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -697.6204824144503,
      "y": 5732.416794363562,
      "width": 523.0111258370534,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bSi",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1948343878,
      "version": 280,
      "versionNonce": 802711878,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "3JHrv3ORs9rvrs7uOkBXh",
          "type": "arrow"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1775370521322,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "序列号和初始化序列号并不是无限增长的，会发生绕回为初\n始值的状态，这意味着无法根据序列号来判断新老数据。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "序列号和初始化序列号并不是无限增长的，会发生绕回为初始值的状态，这意味着无法根据序列号来判断新老数据。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
